nodes.text: Erin Kellyman was born on October 17, 1998  in England. She is an actor known for playing Enfys Nest in Solo: A Star Wars Story, a film which was released on May 25, 2018. Her other acting credits include Cathy in the British television sitcom Raised by Wolves (2013), Éponine Thénardier in the BBC series Les Misérables, and Karli Morgenthau in the Disney+ series The Falcon and the Winter Soldier.
